### Coupon API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN_HERE
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Validate Coupon
POST {{baseUrl}}/coupons/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "WELCOME10",
  "orderAmount": 100
}

### Apply Coupon
POST {{baseUrl}}/coupons/apply
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "WELCOME10"
}

### Admin - Get All Coupons
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/coupons
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Admin - Create Coupon
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/coupons
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "NEWUSER15",
  "discountType": "percentage",
  "discountValue": 15,
  "minOrderAmount": 50,
  "maxDiscount": 30,
  "expiryDate": "2025-12-31",
  "usageLimit": 100,
  "isActive": true
}

### Admin - Update Coupon
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/coupons/COUPON_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isActive": false
}

### Admin - Delete Coupon
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/coupons/COUPON_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
